---
title: Chicken Paillard with Herb Gremolata, Rosemary Potatoes, and Arugula Salad
description: The classic dish is sure to please. Lemon-marinated chicken is butterflied and then seared until golden. Crispy potatoes are complimented by a side of bright arugula salad. We finished with an herby and fragrant gremolata.
